posting_body: ['Ask us about our move-in specials!', 'Enjoy our cozy collection of luxury apartments in Oakland, happily tucked in our little pocket of Temescal.', 'We’re dedicated to bringing you a thoughtful and welcoming sanctuary wrapped in the vibrant surrounds of Temescal.', 'We may be small in numbers (43 total residences), but we’re big in what we bring to the table with our unique floor plan options.', 'That’s our promise, and we want you to hold us to it.', 'Contact us today and schedule a tour to learn more about our wonderful community!', '-Personal Balconies or Patios', '-Online Rent Payments and Service Request', "-Expansive 9' Ceilings", '-Quartz Countertops', '-Views of Oakland Hills & Downtown San Francisco & Oakland', '-Spacious Closets', '-Rooftop Deck with Dining Area and Lounge', '-Controlled Access/Gated', '-Short Distance to BART and AC Transit', '-Fire Pit', '-Recycling', '-Easy Access to Public Parking and Hiking Trails', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
